    <description>When the contact is changed to a Recycled or Unqualified stage updates the opp as CL and sets CL reason. If no open opps, updates the account to inactive prospect and stamp the resell eligible date. JH 8/18/23 updated to include outreach stage Recycled - Not yet qualified
DJ 9/22/23 - Updated No Open SaaS Opp branch to include update Contact Owner to Account Queue. Was not moving contacts out of rep names if Account was already set to Inactive Prospect (ie. was not triggering CL ALA - Update Related Contacts flow)
02.20.2026 - LK - Added to Update the Open Saas Opp to Bypass Champ Field Validation Rule by checking the Bypass Validation Rule = True</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>AccountCustomerType</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>IF(
      CONTAINS({!$Record.Outreach_stage__c},&apos;Unqualified&apos;),
      &apos;Non-Target&apos;, TEXT({!Get_Account.Customer_Type__c})
)</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>AccountRestingPeriod</name>
        <dataType>Date</dataType>
        <expression>IF(
     OR({!$Record.Outreach_stage__c} = &apos;Recycled - Not Yet Qualified&apos;,
    AND(
            {!$Record.Outreach_stage__c} = &apos;Recycled - Not Responding&apos;,
            {!$Record.Spoke_to_DM_Did_Not_Pitch__c} = TRUE
          )), 
          {!$Flow.CurrentDate}+45,
IF(
     AND(
            {!$Record.Outreach_stage__c} = &apos;Recycled - Not Responding&apos;,
            {!$Record.Spoke_to_DM_Did_Not_Pitch__c} = FALSE,
            {!$Record.Spoke_to_Non_DM__c} = TRUE
          ), 
          {!$Flow.CurrentDate}+30,
 IF(
     AND(
            {!$Record.Outreach_stage__c} = &apos;Recycled - Not Responding&apos;,
            {!$Record.Spoke_to_DM_Did_Not_Pitch__c} = FALSE,
            {!$Record.Spoke_to_Non_DM__c} = FALSE
          ), 
          {!$Flow.CurrentDate}+30,
 IF(
      CONTAINS({!$Record.Outreach_stage__c},&apos;Unqualified&apos;),
    {!NULL}, {!$Flow.CurrentDate}+90
))))</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>NULL</name>
        <dataType>Date</dataType>
        <expression>NULL</expression>
    </formulas>
